  "description": "<p>We’re partnering with a well-funded, fast-growing tech company to hire a Senior Infrastructure Engineer to join their team.</p><ul><li>Expert in cloud systems, containerization, automation, and low-latency architectures.</li><li>Build and optimize Kubernetes clusters and core backend services.</li><li>Ensure platform uptime, performance, and security end-to-end.</li><li>Lead incident response to minimize downtime and impact.</li><li>Guide engineers on best practices and infrastructure improvements.</li><li>Partner with leadership to prioritize initiatives and grow the team.</li></ul><p>Reach out to Ayla at ayla@nodeflair.com for a confidential discussion.<br />EA License No: 19S9830</p>",
